snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Aas Paas Episode 21 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 22nd March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Muhammad Iftikhar Iffi
Writer: Samra Bukhari

Cast:
Ali Ansari as Dr. Saham
Laiba Khan as Arshia/Arshi
Samina Ahmed as Aneeqa Begum
Saba Faisal as Seemab
Saife Hasan as Kamal
Sahiba Afzal as Kashifa
Afzal Khan (Jan Rambo) as Ausaf 
Namra Shahid as Shagoofa 
Fahima Awan as Aneela
Faisal Naqvi as Musheer
Alina Chaudhry as Aneela's Mother-in-law 
Nain Sukh as Anooshia/Anooshi
Ahsan Afzal Khan as Ammad
Ahmed Usman as Shehroze

snippet.title: Train -The Unforgettable Journey | Stand up Comedy By Harsh Gujral
snippet.description:
This video is a satirical take on incidents that even Men have to go through in our day to day lives. I have tried to convey a simple message that Men's Safety is never been talked about in this country but deserves equal attention and solutions. Train The Unforgettable Journey has all my experiences and problems i have faced while travelling in a public transport in a funny manner. Please watch the video share with your friends so that there is a message spread in a funny way.
Thank You.

snippet.title: NZ vs PAK 3rd T20I - Cricket Highlights | Pakistan Tour Of New Zealand 2025 | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
In the 3rd T20I of Pakistan’s Tour of New Zealand, Hasan Nawaz smashed a blistering 44-ball century to guide Pakistan to a 9-wicket win in Auckland. Chasing down 205 in just 16 overs, Nawaz’s explosive knock led Pakistan to victory. Earlier, Mohammad Haris contributed a quickfire 41 off 20 balls. Mark Chapman’s 94 helped New Zealand post 204. Watch the thrilling highlights as Pakistan aims to keep their T20I series hopes alive under new captain Salman Ali Agha.

Watch the entire match here: https://bit.ly/NewZealandvsPakistan3rdT20IOnPrime

snippet.description:

Aas Paas Episode 20 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 21st March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

snippet.title: Can I make my Sister’s DREAM Birthday Cake?
snippet.description:
My cousin has the most extra dream birthday cake idea, and I’m putting my drawing skills to the test to bring it to life! Will it turn out as magical as they imagined or turn into a total cake-tastrophe? 🍰😂

Watch till the end to see the final design—should we actually get this cake made for their birthday? Let me know in the comments!

Don’t forget to LIKE, SHARE & SUBSCRIBE for more fun videos! 💖

Lyrics:
Pallavi:
Vela vela vennelantha
Meedha vaali velugunantha
Moyamante nenu entha.. Arere…
Chinni gunde unnadhentha
Haayi nimpi gaalinantha
Oodhamante oopirentha.. Arere…
Kallu rendu pusthakaalu
Bhasha leni aksharaalu
Choopulone ardhamayye.. Anni maatalu…
Mundhu leni aanavaalu
Leniponi kaaranaalu
Kotha kotha onamaalu.. Enni maayalu…
Kathalenno cheppaaru
Kavithalni raasaaru
Kaalaalu dhaataaru
Yuddhaalu chesaaru
Premalo.. Thappu ledhu premalo.. || 2 ||
Charanam 1:
Aakaasham thaakaali ani undha
Naatho raa chupisthaa aa saradhaa
Nelanthaa chuttese veelundhaa
Emundhi premisthe saripodhaa
Aha mabbulanni kommalai
Poolavaana pampithe
Aa vaana peru prema le
Dhaani ooru manamu le
Ye manasuni yemadagaku ye rujuvini.. Oh.. Anthe.. Oh..
|| Kathalenno ||
Charanam 2:
Enthunte entantaa dhooraalu
Rekkallaa ayipothe paadhaalu
Unnaayaa bandhinche dhaaraalu
Oohallo untunte praanaalu
Are ningi loni chukkale
Kindhakochi cherithe
Avi neeku edhuru nilipithe
Undipova ikkade
Jaabili itu cherenu porapaatuna ani.. Oh.. Inthe.. Oh..
|| Kathalenno ||

snippet.title: Empuraan Hyderabad Pressmeet  | Mohanlal | Prithviraj Sukumaran | Sujith Vasudev
snippet.description:
Empuraan Hyderabad Pressmeet  | Mohanlal | Prithviraj Sukumaran | Sujith Vasudev 

#empuraan #empuraanupdate #mohanlal #mohanlalfans #prithvirajsukumaran #manjuwarrier #muraligopy #indrajithsukumaran 

L2: Empuraan also called L2E, is an upcoming Indian Malayalam-language action thriller film directed by Prithviraj Sukumaran, written by Murali Gopy and jointly produced by Lyca Productions and Aashirvad Cinemas. It is the second instalment in a planned trilogy, following the 2019 film Lucifer. The film stars Mohanlal as Khureshi-Ab'raam / Stephen Nedumpally, alongside Prithviraj Sukumaran, Tovino Thomas, Indrajith Sukumaran, Manju Warrier, Saniya Iyappan, Saikumar, Baiju Santhosh, Fazil and Sachin Khedekar reprising their roles from the original.

Lucifer was always intended to be a series from its inception, originally conceived as a three-part film. The first part was made into the film Lucifer. The success of the first film led to the decision to proceed with the second instalment in the series. Murali took the opportunity to expand the scale and scope of Empuraan. The screenplay was finalised in July 2022, and pre-production began the following month. Lyca Productions joined as a producer in 2023, marking their debut in Malayalam, alongside Aashirvad Cinemas, the producer of the original. The film's music was composed by Deepak Dev.

👉 *In this reaction, we cover:*
- The intensity and energy of the *Sikandar* trailer  
- Salman Khan’s larger-than-life presence and action sequences  
- Rashmika Mandanna’s charm and chemistry with Salman  
- Sathyaraj and Kajal Aggarwal’s impactful roles  
- The music, visuals, and overall vibe of the trailer

Bharti Tv Podcast Mein Aapka Hardik Swagat Hai!

Aaj Ke Khaas Episode Mein, Bharti Aur Harsh Ke Saath Jud Rahi Hain Ek Incredible Personality Jinhone Apni Honesty Aur Resilience Se Sabke Dil Jeet Liye — Rubina Dilaik..!

Rubina Share Karengi Apne Life Ke Unknown Chapters, Career Struggles, Life Challenges Aur Bhi Bohut Kuch Unheard, Exclusive, Sirf Humare Saath.

Unhone Bataya Kaise, Life Ke Kisi Bhi Problems Mein Unki Family And Parents Ka Unconditional Pyaar & Support Ek Constant Motivation Raha Hai. Saath Hi Abhinav Shukla, Jaise Life Partner Ka Hona Unka Sabse Bada Strength Hai, Jiske Liye Woh Khud Ko Bohut Lucky Manti Hain. 

Yeh Sirf Ek Celebrity Ki Kahani Nahi, Balki Puri Journey Hai, Jo Unhone Jiya Hai Aur Aaj Humare Saath Share Karengi.

snippet.title: Bathroom ka Evolution | Stand-up Comedy by Amit Tandon
snippet.description:
Bringing my New Stand-up Special ‘Halwa’ to a city near you.

UK & Europe - 3rd May to 8th June
Australia & New Zealand – 19th September to 28th September
Singapore & Dubai – To be announced soon!

Tickets on shows.tandonamit.com/shows (All upcoming international tour dates and tickets)

Ever wondered how our bathroom habits have changed over time? In this hilarious stand-up set, Amit Tandon takes you through the evolution of the bathroom experience. ”Bathroom Ka Evolution" is a relatable comedy ride filled with every desi household’s quirks and global bathroom truths that we rarely discuss openly!

Subscribe to Amit Tandon's channel and click the bell icon for updates on more comedy specials and hilarious insights!

Written & Performed by - Amit Tandon
Follow me on Instagram : instagram.com/amitandon17

Production House: KNCK KNCK Productions
Management: Collective Artists Network

Technical Director & DOP: Arbaaz Nasser
Line Producer: Vedang Devlekar

Camera Operators:
Aditi Hirani
Sakshat Shetty
Kedar Jadhav
Shivlal
Ritesh

Gimbal Operation:
Suraj Kumar
Saddam Mandal

Associate Producers:
Alina Rajan
Iqra Nasser

BTS: Shreyansh Mehta

Post Production Studio: Knck Knck
Editing: Iqra Nasser & Arbaaz Nasser
Sound Mix & Master: Yash Rajiv Barse
Colorist: Arbaaz Nasser
Captions: Kaustubh Kadam
Motion Graphics: Kartikey Chudasma


Amit Tandon’s signature family-friendly humor shines throughout this video, blending Hindi and English (Hinglish) to connect with everyone. Whether you call it a bathroom or a washroom, you’ll find Amit's observational comedy spot-on.

About Amit Tandon: Known as the "family man" of comedy, Amit is one of India's most beloved comedians. With over 200 million views and fans worldwide, he's famed for his clean, hilarious hindi & hinglish comedy content along with his Netflix special "Family Tandoncies."

IPL 2025 fever getting to you? Or taking a quick break from Jee Mains prep? Amit’s relatable comedy is the perfect way to unwind and recharge!

Share your funniest bathroom story in the comments! 😂🛁

#AmitTandon #StandUpComedy #BathroomKaEvolution

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4352 - Sunderlal ne Diya Jethalal ko Surprise?!| Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah| तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Gokuldham Society | Gada Electronics

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta

Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi

Jethalal is excited about his meeting with Hussain, but repeated delays prevent him from leaving for the office. Will he reach on time?

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: WATERMELON JELLY | Fresh Colorful Fruit Jelly Recipe Making in Village | Agar Agar Jelly Cooking
snippet.description: This video showcases the making of a healthy, fresh, and natural fruit jelly using a variety of colorful fruits, sugar, and agar agar. The combination of fresh fruits adds natural sweetness and a delightful texture, while agar agar helps create a perfect jelly consistency. This refreshing dessert is not only visually stunning but also a light and healthy treat, made using simple ingredients without any artificial additives. Watch the entire process as we prepare, set, and slice this beautiful jelly, bringing out the flavors of nature’s best ingredients in a traditional village-style preparation.

snippet.title: தக்காளி குருமா ஒரு முறை இப்படி செய்ங்க ! மாவு தீரும் வரை சாப்பிடுவாங்க !! Idli tomato kurma recipe
snippet.description:
ingredients;

Tomato - 2 Nos
coconut -1/4 cup
Ginger - 2 inch
garlic cloves - 5 Nos.
poppy seeds - 3/4 tea spoon 
fennel seeds - one teaspoon 
Roasted chana dal - 2 table spoon 
oil - two table spoon 
spices 
onion - one Medium size 
curry leaves 
kulambu chilli powder - 2 table spoon 
turmeric powder - 1/2 table spoon 
salt to taste.

தேவையான பொருட்கள்;
தக்காளி - 2
தேங்காய் - 1/4 கப் 
இஞ்சி - 2 இன்ச் 
பூண்டு பற்கள் - 5
கச கச - 3/4 தேக்கரண்டி 
சோம்பு - ஒரு தேக்கரண்டி 
பொட்டு கடலை - 2 மேசை கரண்டி 
எண்ணெய் - 2 மேசை கரண்டி 
மசாலா பொருட்கள் 
வெங்காயம் - ஒன்று நறுக்கியது
குழம்பு மிளகாய்த்தூள் - 2 மேசை கரண்டி 
மஞ்சள் தூள் - அரை தேக்கரண்டி 
கருவேப்பிலை 
தேவையான அளவு உப்பு.


செய்முறை:

வெங்காயத்தை நீளவாக்கில் நறுக்கிக் கொள்ளவும்

மிக்ஸியில் துருவிய தேங்காய், பொட்டு கடலை, இஞ்சி, பூண்டு,கசகசா, சோம்பு,  நறுக்கிய தக்காளி ஆகியவற்றை போட்டு விழுதாக அரைத்துக் கொள்ளவும்.

வாணலியில் எண்ணெய் விட்டு காய்ந்ததும் பட்டை கிராம்பு மசாலா தாளித்து மீதமுள்ள நறுக்கிய வெங்காயத்தைப் போட்டு சிறிது நேரம் வதக்கவும்.

வெங்காயம் வதங்கியதும் கருவேப்பிலை போட்டு நன்றாக வதக்கவும்.

வெங்காயம், நன்றாக வதங்கியதும் அரைத்து வைத்துள்ள விழுதினை சேர்த்து மேலும் சிறிது தண்ணீர் சேர்த்து கொதிக்க விடவும்.

கலவை நன்றாக கொதித்ததும் உப்பு சேர்த்து கிளறி விட்டு இறக்கவும்

சுவையான செட்டிநாடு தக்காளி குருமா தயார்....

localized.description:
ingredients;

Tomato - 2 Nos
coconut -1/4 cup
Ginger - 2 inch
garlic cloves - 5 Nos.
poppy seeds - 3/4 tea spoon 
fennel seeds - one teaspoon

oil - two table spoon 
spices

curry leaves

குழம்பு மிளகாய்த்தூள் - 2 மேசை கரண்டி 
மஞ்சள் தூள் - அரை தேக்கரண்டி

Episode 4351: Hyderabad Ka Order
--------------------------------------------------------
Bagha and Nattu Kaka are thrilled to see early customers at Gada Electronics. Later, Jethalal gets a call from Hussain in Hyderabad about his order.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4351 - Jethalal ke Jaal me Phasi Bawri?!| Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah| तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Gokuldham Society | Gada Electronic 

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
